   "body" : "Don't have `cs_wallet` locked while calling each `context.wallet_load_fns`. A load handler can always lock `cs_wallet` if needed.\r\n\r\nThe lock was added in 1c7e25db0c to satisfy TSAN. With 44c430ffac most of the code requiring the lock is in `CWallet::AttachChain`. A comment is added to warn about wallets_mutex and cs_wallet lock ordering.",
